---
description: Loop Engineering rules for Playwright test agents — always verify with npx playwright test before claiming done
globs:
  - specs/**
  - tests/**
  - docs/LOOP-ENGINEERING.md
---

Read `docs/LOOP-ENGINEERING.md` before plan, generate, or heal work. Doc map: `docs/README.md`.

Master loop: Plan → Generate → Run → Heal → Verify. Never treat a single prompt as complete without running `npx playwright test`.

Use `/goal` and `/loop` templates from LOOP-ENGINEERING.md. Update `.loop/run-log.json` each iteration.

Healer max 3 attempts per test. Master loop max 2 iterations per feature.
